quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,“Ndikulumbilira akavalo othamanga ali ndi phuma
  100,2,“Ndi otulutsa moto ku zikhotwa (pomenyetsa miyendo m’miyala)
  100,3,“Ndi othira nkhondo adani mmawa (dzuwa lisadatuluke)
  100,4,“Ndi kuulutsa fumbi lambiri (kwa adani) nthawi imeneyo
  100,5,“Ndikulowelera mkatikati mwa adani
  100,6,"“Ndithu munthu ali wokanira Mbuye wake, (sathokoza Allah pa zimene amdalitsa nazo)"
  100,7,“Ndithudi iye pa zimenezi ndi mboni (yodzichitira yekha kupyolera mzochitachita zake)
  100,8,“Ndipo ndithu iye ndiwokonda chuma kwambiri (ndiponso ngwamsulizo)
  100,9,“Kodi sakudziwa zikadzatulutsidwa za m’manda
  100,10,“Ndikudzasonkhanitsidwa ndi kuonekera poyera zomwe zidali m’mitima
  100,11,“Ndithu tsiku limenelo Mbuye wawo adzawadziwa kwambiri (ndikuwalongosolera zonse zochita zawo)